  "instructions": [
    "Rinse the bulgur and soak it in water for 4 hours.",
    "Drain the bulgur and mix it with ground almonds, bay leaves, thyme, and a pinch of salt.",
    "In a separate pan, heat olive oil and saut\u00121 garlic until fragrant.",
    "Add shio cure and coconut water to the pan and bring to a boil.",
    "Reduce heat and simmer for 10 minutes.",
    "In a steamer basket, combine the bulgur mixture and steamer basket with the coconut water mixture.",
    "Steam for 10 minutes.",
    "Garnish with parsley, lemon juice, and a sprinkle of salt."
